29 to either lodge above, are exempted from paying all state fees
30 and taxes.
31 (2) Any county or municipality may exempt the entities
32 in (1) from the payment of county or municipal sales and use
33 taxes in accordance with Section 40-23-4.01, Code of Alabama
34 1975.
35 (4) The exemptions provided by this subsection are
36 effective beginning October 1, 2027.
37 (c)The Most Worshipful Prince Hall Grand Lodge Free and
38 Accepted Masons of Alabama and the Most Worshipful Grand Lodge
39 F. and A.M. of Alabama, shall provide the Department of
40 Revenue with a list of all subordinate lodges on an annual
41 basis.
42 (d) The Department of Revenue shall adopt rules for the
43 implementation and administration of this act."
44 Section 2. This act shall become effective on September
45 1, 2026.
